law.footnote: FOOTNOTE(S): --- (1) --- Editor's note— Section 1 of Ord. No. 81-48, adopted May 5, 1981, added a chapter to the Code, but did not specify a number. At the editor's discretion, it was added as Ch. 26D, §§ 26D-1—26D-12, as amended by Ord. No. 82-28, adopted April 20, 1982. Ord. No. 82-103, § 1, adopted Oct. 19, 1982, repealed Ch. 26D, which had pertained to the South Florida Sports Authority. (Back)
